data.text:
@chris1harris Hi I am sorry to hear your luggage was delayed. If you have not yet reported your bag, please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 you can track your bags here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU
Please contact the airport for further assistance https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
Kind regards, Rebecka

@RichyP85 Hi! At first glance, that crate looks excellent. You can find more regulations and rules it has to follow here: https://t.co/xcfWzNbM01
You are always welcome contact us on Customer service for further assistance: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards, Rebecka

@teripost Hi, I am sorry to hear that the bags were delayed. You can track the missing bags here: https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU alternatively find a phone number to call here: https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2
If you need to set up a PIR please do so here: https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3

Kind regards, Rebecka

@fyrbarnsfar Hej! Eftersom att vi erbjuder resmål över hela världen så har vi valt att använda roterande hälsningsfraser från våra destinationer vid inloggning till EuroBonus, för mig exempelvis stod det "Grüezi Anton" idag, och imorgon lär det stå något annat.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@GaryJust67 Hi, as the rates look today the excess weight fee for baggage between 28.1 kg - 32.0 kg is 80 EUR per baggage and per one-way on flights within Europe. If possible, it will be cheaper for you to pack in two baggages each and buy an extra baggage per person.

Best regards,
Anton.

@jasimanski Hello, I'm sorry to hear that your luggage was delayed. To request reimbursement/compensation for this please open a claim with our Customer Care at https://t.co/kDAXvXUXIa

Best regards,
Anton.

@BluegrassBrooks Hi, I'm sorry to hear that your luggage is delayed. To make a report for delayed luggage please use our web form https://t.co/uHX1YFCLU3 - If you wish to contact baggage service directly you can find phone numbers at https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

Best regards,
Anton.

@MaxWilson1001 Hi, it is not possible to purchase Fast Track separately as a travel extra unfortunately, Fast Track is something that is included in your travel class (SAS Plus / Business) or in your EuroBonus/Star Alliance membership if you are Gold or higher.

Best regards,
Anton.

@SAntonishen Hi, I'm sorry to hear that your bicycle was not transported correctly during your transfer. Please contact our Baggage service support and they can help you take a look at what has happened and what the solution is https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

Best regards,
Anton.

@sondrelercheno Hej, vi beklagar att ert bagage är försenat, vänligen kontakta vår Baggage service support för att se om de har mer information om vart ert bagage finns lokaliserat i nuläget, telefonummer till Baggage Service finns på https://t.co/ZV9bTO3uo2

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@spaulding071968 Hi OC in the OC
You do not require facemask. If your destination has any specific requirements regarding covid vaccination you can find it via this link https://t.co/YhT9mVc7De
Kind regards /Anna

@SunderlandDiane Hi, we have a special assistance service which we can book for hidden disabilities as well. Please contact us on FB Messenger or livechat to request this https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@karinaasb Hej, SAS Café lounge på Flesland är för tillfället stängd tills vidare på grund av en kommande ombyggnation av flygplatsen. Vi beklagar obekvämligheterna men i dagsläget vet vi inte när lounge på Flesland kommer att vara tillgänglig igen.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@SunderlandDiane Hi, we appreciate that some of our customers sometimes need a little more help. You can read more about which kind of assistances we can book at https://t.co/y8n0APD6Il Contact customer service to request the assistance at least 48h before departure.

Best regards,
Anton.

@bex_hb Hi do you wish to fly from PSP Palm Springs? I don't believe PAL Palanquero can be booked through us. I recommend you to contact our sales and service on the phone for help with booking, and checking availability for a 16h stop in CPH https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@utvik Jag förstår, beklagar att ni har fått vänta på svar länge. Kontakta oss via chatt eller telefon så skickar vi en påminnelse till customer care att svara på ert ärende.
Vänliga hälsningar,
Stina

@hareshtrishna I understand that this has caused difficulties for you. You are welcome to make a claim on: https://t.co/kDAXvXUXIa If you are entitled to compensation will be decided by our customer care department who handles the claim. 
Kind regards,
Stina

@warren_munger Hi, if your passport only contains one given name the ticket must be booked through customer service, so in this case I must ask you to try to call us again, or contact us on livechat again and say that you want to book a ticket.

Best regards,
Anton.

@Morpain Hej, vi beklagar om du upplever problem på vår hemsida. Kontakta oss gärna på FB Messenger elller livechat https://t.co/RDEH7uxbwJ med mer information om hur och vad du försöker boka så kan vi hjälpa dig att felsöka problemet.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@warren_munger Hi, if you are not able to reach us on the phone I would recommend you to write to us on Facebook Messenger, or livechat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@Janbsagmo Hej, jag känner inte till något om att Diamondkortet ska försvinna om du menar rent generellt, har du frågor angående ditt enskilda konto så rekommenderar jag att du kontaktar oss på Messenger eller livechatt https://t.co/cIkJt9kPnF

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@peterrost Hello, if you wish to send us a complaint and/or suggestion regarding the meal that was served on your flight, please use our feedback form at https://t.co/xMt9zSrqJc

Best regards,
Anton.

@warren_munger Hi, 
I'm sorry you are experiencing issues booking your flight. You are welcome to contact us by phone for help with your booking. 
Kind regards, Stina

@JonatanMarc Hej, i de fallen då man blir ofrivilligt ombokad, eller flyget blir försenat och kundservice har stängt för dagen så får man ta detta med personalen på flygplatsen så kan de hjälpa en att kolla på eventuell ombokning till nästa avgång.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@JeremyGeorgeJG Hello, sometimes the wait time on the phone can be longer than usual, our customer service is working as quickly as possible to take all calls. If you did not get through on the phone you can try our live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj 

Best regards,
Anton.

@Scott_Helme Hello, please contact our livechat or phone support with your booking details and they can help you take a look at the refund https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@cardiffdanuk Hello, the bag drop generally opens 2-3 hours before departure.

Best regards,
Anton.

@casterlyss Hello, the bag drop generally opens 2-3 hours before your departure.

Best regards,
Anton.

@patripfr Hello, we are unfortunately not able to assist with individual cases over Twitter. Please contact our livechat or phone support for help with your case https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@mascott22 Hi! We do have vegan meals on our Intercontinental flights. But you need to contact us the latest 24 h before your flight in order to add it to your booking. You can contact us by chat or phone in this link. https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best Regards
Fatima

@casterlyss Hi! We recommend that you are at the airport as soon as you can, make sure that you have dropped your bag as soon as possible to ensure you make it through the security. Bag opens between 2-4 hours before the departure, depending on your destination.  
Kind regards,
Rebecka

@jennagedwards Hello!
Yes, that's right. For safety reasons, no blankets, jackets or similar be placed over the legs or in any other place where they may be away in the event of an evacuation of the aircraft.

Kind regards, Anja!

@frederikjarl Hej!
Vi garanterar inte att ett specifikt flyg kommer att gå som planerat. Detta nämns i våra transportvillkor. Alla flygbolag har en liknande klausul i sina transportvillkor. https://t.co/mm6elp50w0 Du är välkommen att kontakta oss om du vill kika på andra alternativ. 

//Anja

@NadaZeljkovic Hello!
If the web form does not work for you, I would ask you to call the baggage service for the airport where you landed. You can find baggage service contact information here: https://t.co/ZV9bTNLSZs

Kind regards, Anja!

@wahl_kathrin Hello!
If lounge access for silver members is also offered this summer, this will be published under member offers on our website, I recommend that you yo keep an eye here. https://t.co/z8g4WpiWk2. 

Kind regards, Anja!

@ml_heise Hej! 
Du är välkommen att kontakta oss så kikar vi närmare på ditt ärende. Du finner våra kontaktuppgifter här: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Tack för att du kontaktar oss, hälsningar Anja!

@dakar85 Hi,
I suggest that you check in online on both flights all the way to the final destination and if all flights are with the same flight company then it should arrive at Reykjavík with you. If you need further information, please contact us on phone or live chat.

Best/ Emilia

@rolpos Hello!
The chat is working, I suggest that you try to contact us again either via phone or by live chat. If there's a queue on the phone then we apologize for this and ask you to try another time if you do not have the possibility to wait. Keep in mind our opening hours.

/Emilia
